      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, i'm studying for my structural mechanics exam. can u explain why we actually need to add steel rebar to concrete foundations? like why isnt the concrete itself enough to handle the loads? im a bit confused about the relationship between compressive and tensile strength here.",
